    "text": "Halting Enrichment of Russian Oligarchs and Industry Allies of Moscow's Schemes to Leverage its Abject Villainy Abroad Act of 2023 or the HEROIAM SLAVA Act of 2023\n\nThis bill requires the President to exercise certain authorities to block all transactions in property belonging to any entity owned or controlled by Russia if such property is within the United States or in the possession or control of a U.S. person."
